dBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:20:50.000Z","msg":"<code>路政署發言人強調，路政署駐工地人員綜合檢視個案詳情及研究該專家的意見後，確認有關混凝土符合相關質量要求。 此</code><br />\n質乜春量啫 有人話少咗水泥咩 係水泥質素出事喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00edb81bff36877c96bb8809ef0620ff4896480","tid":974033,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:48:13.000Z","msg":"aecom科左水畀hk01?"},{"pid":"03f5830327cbace0bc28a28d2d81eaf07c63c5a2","tid":974033,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:00:00.000Z","msg":"岩啦港島咁多離地中產<br />\n少咁D呢堆人香港會好得多<br />\n一物治一物<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}